{"tid":803689,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"（求救）好大壓力。就黎有精神病","createTime":"2018-09-02T12:50:34.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-04T09:57:41.000Z","uid":18227,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"56baf820157667c00928d0b898ca30e9a4561553","tid":803689,"uid":18227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-02T12:50:34.000Z","msg":"獨仔一個，屋企住公屋<br />\n<br />\n老豆老母關係非常唔好<br />\n<br />\n老豆年過60，仲係咁爛賭，一個錢都唔會留身，完全唔為屋企同自己打算<br />\n<br />\n老母體弱多病（最近又入院），冇讀書做唔到咩工。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我出黎做野冇耐搵得萬靚蚊。但比佢2個一直比壓力我。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n又唔敢同朋友分享。"},{"pid":"70c2e1356493433f3e52a56a5c09ce2aafd54934","tid":803689,"uid":41368,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-02T13:03:31.000Z","msg":"搵幾個人自己出嚟夾個工廈單位住"},{"pid":"52b3910b89877f0c32fcf7136e9faa052752f5c9","tid":803689,"uid":18227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"70c2e1356493433f3e52a56a5c09ce2aafd54934","tid":803689,"uid":41368,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-02T13:03:31.000Z","msg":"搵幾個人自己出嚟夾個工廈單位住"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-02T13:13:44.000Z","msg":"出黎住應該解決唔到。<br />\n<br />\n屋企所有費租金 水電煤都係我負責。<br />\n<br />\n就黎連佢地生活費都要我比埋。"},{"pid":"652bb0ab446fe94803eb4bec2518faa17521de19","tid":803689,"uid":35815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-02T13:49:34.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"001c442aae6f97269d328d4a04277648ea9a4544","tid":803689,"uid":180156,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-02T13:51:46.000Z","msg":"窮人生仔正仆街"},{"pid":"99682e0c259e80d5f1c977c25e8363da676bab3f","tid":803689,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-02T14:27:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"06063892c3bbbcac18bb96ffe1a36a5017444caa","tid":803689,"uid":179649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-02T14:34:17.000Z","msg":"點一直比壓力你？<br />\n老豆我明，佢既行為的確令你好無助<br />\n一係同佢講你既處境，叫佢唔好再財<br />\n但你媽入左院我